{
  "stem": "27770.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The mother, even if they would tell the mother that you go to the gas chamber, and this way you will be survive-- you will be survived, she wouldn't believe it.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "She would take the child and she would go to the gas chamber with the child.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So that's what they did.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They meant to help the people.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But that's why it was such a hateness between those Hungarians and the Polish, because this Polish guy took away my child and didn't let me go wherever with my child.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So right away started the selection.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Mengele, who was the-- Dr.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Mengele, the famous Josef Mengele, whom I met almost every week or second week, because he was studying us, because he himself had a pair of twins-- boys-- who are still today in Germany.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They have a big factory.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And now is a big sign that says Mengele Factory.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It's a shame there is such a thing that they allow.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But that's how the world is today.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So he took-- he came, made the selection, right, left, right, left.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Then he was looking for the twins.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Of course, somebody told my uncle, told my father, listen Bentzion-- Bentzion was my father's name-- your children are twins, and I'm sure they're not going to go to hard labor, so report.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Of course, my father was angry because he was that I should be with him.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And my mother should be with my sister.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "But we didn't ask too much, it went fast.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "They took all the twins.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And, of course, they went to the crematorium, and we went to a hospital department and there they started the study on us.",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
